description:
Ultimate 80's Cartoon Collection (First Episodes)





About this Torrent


This is something i have taken a lot of time in making as a torrent for all users throughout
the torrent world who were fans of cartoons from early 80's to beginning of the 1990's 
personally this brings back some fantastic memories for myself and im hoping it does 
the same for you all and brings back that inner child... Things have changed since then
and to be honest we all know cartoons will never be the same as they were back in the day.
-
i have done my best to put in as many of the well known and enjoyable cartoons as possible
every one of these episodes are the first of the series in the chain but be aware before 
downloading i cant remember them all so please appreciate the fact that this has never been
done before by any uploader.
-
enjoy and please dont forget to like and leave a comment
